<div class="article pbl right-col size3of4 cf">



        <h1 class="header-skin header-structure">Staff and Facilities</h1>


	<div class="page-tabgroup">
			


<div class="page-tabs ">

        <div class="page-tab">
            <a href="/conservatoire/acting/staff-and-facilities/our-staff" class="page-tab__link  page-tab__link--active">Our Staff</a>
        </div>
        <div class="page-tab">
            <a href="/conservatoire/acting/staff-and-facilities/facilities" class="page-tab__link ">Facilities</a>
        </div>

</div>
			
		<div class="page-tab__content">
			
    <div class="relative ">


            <div class="content-block">

<p><img alt="BSA Staff and Facilities" class="block mbm pas grey-box scalable" data-source="5bdcc87b-b810-e711-80cf-005056831842" onerror="missingImages({imgTag : this})" src="https://bcu.imgix.net/paper-installation1-crop-131484739071790659.jpg?auto=format&fm=jpg"></p>
<div class="grid">
<div class="left-col size2of3">
<p class="lead">Here, you can see a list of key staff from Royal Birmingham Conservatoire's Acting department.</p>
<p>Royal Birmingham Conservatoire Acting has a management team made up of senior academic staff and professional services managers. The faculty executive body oversees the school management team.</p>
<p>Course Directors are responsible for the delivery of each course with the Academic Administration Managers responsible for the quality assurance and regulations of assessments.</p>
<p>RBC Acting has a number of specialist departments including Acting, Voice, Singing, Movement and Production which are led by individual Heads of Department.</p>
</div>
<div class="left-col size1of3">
<div class="pull-out-primary">
<h4><span class="icon-users gamma pan mrm" aria-hidden="true"></span> Meet our Staff</h4>
<div class="pull-out-primary-sub">
<h5 class="black">Want to know more about our acting tutors?</h5>
<p>Our students are taught by academic staff with a real passion for the subjects they teach - take a closer look.</p>
<p class="mbn"><a class="bcu-button block text-center" href="http://bcu.ac.uk/acting/applications/meet-birmingham-school-of-actings-staff">A-Z tutor list</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="j-slide-reveal collapsible pam mts closed">
<div class="clear-fix"><abbr class="inline mrm icon-plus-squared"></abbr>
<h4 class="man inline">Performance</h4>
</div>
</div>
<div class="js-hidden j-slide-reveal-content">
<div class="grid">
<div class="left size1of2">
<h4>Acting</h4>
<p><strong><a href="http://bcu.ac.uk/acting/applications/meet-birmingham-school-of-actings-staff/stephen-simms">Prof. Stephen Simms</a>:</strong> Head of Acting, Director<br><strong><a href="http://bcu.ac.uk/acting/applications/meet-birmingham-school-of-actings-staff/daniele-sanderson">Danièle Sanderson</a>: </strong>Head of Undergraduate Studies (Acting) and Course Director - BA Acting<br> <strong><a href="/conservatoire/acting/further-info/tutor-list/alex-taylor">Alex Taylor</a>: </strong>Head of Postgraduate Studies - Acting and Course Director MFA Acting<br> <strong><a href="http://bcu.ac.uk/acting/applications/meet-birmingham-school-of-actings-staff/lise-olson">Lise Olson</a>: </strong>Course Director - MA/PgDip Acting, Director<br><strong><a href="http://bcu.ac.uk/acting/applications/meet-birmingham-school-of-actings-staff/alex-taylor">Alex Taylor</a>: </strong>Head of Postgraduate Studies - Acting and Course Director - MA/PgDip Professional Voice Practice and MFA Acting<br><strong><a href="/conservatoire/acting/further-info/tutor-list/robert-miles">Robert Miles</a></strong>: Course Director, Foundation Course in Acting <br><strong><a href="/conservatoire/acting/further-info/tutor-list/paola-botham">Dr Paola Botham:</a></strong> Tutor<br><strong><a href="http://bcu.ac.uk/acting/applications/meet-birmingham-school-of-actings-staff/louise-papillon">Louise Papillon</a>: </strong>Acting & Physical Skills Tutor, Director and Librarian<br><strong>Andrew Potter: </strong>Acting Tutor, Director<br><strong><a href="http://bcu.ac.uk/acting/applications/meet-birmingham-school-of-actings-staff/clifford-milner">Clifford Milner</a>: </strong>Senior Acting Tutor Recorded Media, Director</p>
<h5>Visiting Acting Tutors</h5>
<p><strong>Liam Clarke: </strong>Acting Tutor<br><strong>George Naylor: </strong>Acting Tutor<br><strong>John Partridge: </strong>Acting Tutor</p>
</div>
<div class="left-col size1of2">
<h4>Singing</h4>
<p><strong>Rob Miles:</strong> Head of Singing<br><strong><a class="no-icon" href="https://www.bcu.ac.uk/conservatoire/acting/further-info/tutor-list/iain-jackson">Iain Jackson</a>:</strong> Resident Accompanist</p>
<h5>Visiting Singing Tutors</h5>
<p><strong>SJ Bourne: </strong>Singing Tutor<br><strong>Aimée Whatson:</strong> Singing Tutor<br><strong>Richard Hughes</strong><br><strong>Angela Moran: </strong> Accompanist<br><strong>Joe Robinson: </strong> Accompanist, M/D, Ensemble Singing Tutor<br><strong>Ben Wiles: </strong> Accompanist, M/D, Singing Tutor<br><br></p>
</div>
</div>
<h4>Voice</h4>
<p><strong><a href="http://bcu.ac.uk/acting/applications/meet-birmingham-school-of-actings-staff/alex-taylor">Alex Taylor</a>: </strong>MA Professional Voice Practice Course Director, Head of Voice<br><strong><a class="no-icon" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/simon-ratcliffe-7b298011">Simon Ratcliffe</a>:</strong><strong> </strong>Voice Tutor</p>
<h5>Visiting Voice Tutors</h5>
<p><strong><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/lottie-williams-burrell-271688123/">Lottie Williams-Burrell</a>: </strong>Voice Tutor</p>
<h4>Movement</h4>
